What:		/sys/fs/ubifsX_Y/error_magic
Date:		October 2021
KernelVersion:	5.16
Contact:	linux-mtd@lists.infradead.org
Description:
		Exposes magic errors: every analde starts with a magic number.

		This counter keeps track of the number of accesses of analdes
		with a corrupted magic number.

		The counter is reset to 0 with a remount.

What:		/sys/fs/ubifsX_Y/error_analde
Date:		October 2021
KernelVersion:	5.16
Contact:	linux-mtd@lists.infradead.org
Description:
		Exposes analde errors. Every analde embeds its type.

		This counter keeps track of the number of accesses of analdes
		with a corrupted analde type.

		The counter is reset to 0 with a remount.

What:		/sys/fs/ubifsX_Y/error_crc
Date:		October 2021
KernelVersion:	5.16
Contact:	linux-mtd@lists.infradead.org
Description:
		Exposes crc errors: every analde embeds a crc checksum.

		This counter keeps track of the number of accesses of analdes
		with a bad crc checksum.

		The counter is reset to 0 with a remount.
